name: Manulife Smart International Defensive Equity ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to achieve long-term capital appreciation. Fund investing primarily in a diversified portfolio of international securities while also seeking to reduce overall market sensitivity. Any exposure that the portion of the portfolio of the ETF attributable to the Unhedged Units may have to foreign currencies will not be hedged back to the Canadian dollar.
